Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.89,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}それ誰のルール
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.49,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}迷わずにdive in dive in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.85,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Stand up 壊してく the nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.44,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}解けないSilentなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.86,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}その口にルージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.19,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}エンドロールまでI say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.06,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 冗談じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.92,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Nighty night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:16.60,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.12,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}捨ててきてrulers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.95,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.49,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}One day…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.89,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:20.53,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oops! I killed another morning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:24.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一個人天花板 盯著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:29.19,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}包羅萬象什麼的 無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.36,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}腦袋裡面載入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是不是不可能的嘛
Comment: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.67,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.85,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.44,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.86,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.19,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.06,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 這不是玩笑
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Nighty night
Comment: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:16.60,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.12,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}去捨棄掉吧 rulers
