Comment: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}One day…
Comment: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
